article.headline: Bryant knocks off Howard 67-61
article.story: SMITHFIELD, R.I. -- — Earl Timberlake's 19 points helped Bryant defeat Howard 67-61 on Monday night. Timberlake added five rebounds for the Bulldogs (3-3). Connor Withers scored 15 points, shooting 5 for 7, including 4 for 5 from beyond the arc. Seth Towns and Shy Odom scored 16 points apiece for the Bison (2-4). Towns grabbed nine rebounds and Bryce Harris added 11 points and eight rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
